{"tid":1990886,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發時空．沈旭暉 002】Decontextualization：「高尚情操」與「歧視」歪論","createTime":"2020-04-27T04:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T04:57:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"df2a36fcd0fc79725c501cbe803d31e5465c89eb","tid":1990886,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T04:57:32.000Z","msg":"【突發時空．沈旭暉 002】Decontextualization：「高尚情操」與「歧視」歪論<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/87yGQUb_FTA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F87yGQUb_FTA&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4NeKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=81ccb1bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/87yGQUb_FTA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n堅離地球 &middot; 沈旭暉<br />\n75.6K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n當特區政府法官以「高尚情操」演繹連儂牆的斬人兇手，反映了甚麼結構？與此同時，亦有知識份子以上綱上線方式演繹「歧視」，背後又有甚麼玄機？兩者之間，都有一種「decontextualization」非情境化、非脈絡化的演繹。但「decontextualization」也有兩類，一種其實在顛覆現有超穩定結構，類似一戰後的達達主義，可以促進社會進步；另一種恰恰相反，卻在呼應強權的維穩工作。日後這類非脈絡化的處理，恐怕成為常態，必須有所警惕。<br />\n<br />\nSimon 沈旭暉 堅離地 Social Media ▶<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4NeKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=498ba213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsimon.diplo...&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4NeKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=d22a47b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/simonshen_glos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsimonshen_glos&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4NeKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=06a4e4f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/simonshen_glos</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"https://simonshen.blog/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A